import React from 'react' const DataOutput = (props) => { const { name, artistName, duration, popularity, audioFeatures } = props const {danceability, energy, key, mode, speechiness, acousticness, instrumentalness, liveness, valence, tempo, } = audioFeatures return (

{name}

by {artistName}

Duration: {duration}
Key: {key} Mode: {mode} Tempo: {tempo}
Popularity: {popularity}
Danceability: {danceability}
Energy: {energy}
Speechiness: {speechiness}
Acousticness: {acousticness}
Instrumentalness: {instrumentalness}
Liveness: {liveness}
Valence: {valence}
) } export default DataOutput
